title: The sea spray carries secrets for
description: The sea spray carries secrets for those brave enough to seek them. A faint echo from the forgotten past beckons you towards the coast. Your journey leads to the Point Mendocino Trail, where your task is to explore its winding paths. Seek out what the ocean has patiently guarded within its ancient embrace.

trailLocation.title: Point Mendocino Trail
trailLocation.description: A scenic hiking area with trails perfect for outdoor adventures and nature exploration. Rated 4.9/5 by visitors.
